comments.content:
Looks like sqlalchemy-migrate is complaining about missing migration 83.  We currently only have migrations 133-203 in the latest Havana dev code.

Do you have an existing older OpenStack install on this computer?  What version?  Migration 82 was the first migration of Folsom, and it collapsed all the previous Essex migrations into one.  Migration 83 was the first "regular" migration of Folsom.

dpkg indicates Debian or one of its derivitives, but can you provide your Linux distribution and its version, and what command you ran to get this output?
